com.amplifyframework.logging

Class JavaLoggingPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.logging.LoggingPlugin<java.lang.Void>
      • com.amplifyframework.logging.JavaLoggingPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CategoryTypeable, Plugin<java.lang.Void>, LoggingCategoryBehavior

    public final class JavaLoggingPlugin
extends LoggingPlugin<java.lang.Void>
    Implementation of the LoggingCategoryBehavior designed for use by unit tests, which emits logs via System.out.println().
